data.description: In the heart of Jacksonville, situated on a corner lot, you'll fall in love with the open kitchen area.  Off the kitchen, is a flex space which would be perfect for an office, toy room, or reading area. Upstairs, is the master bedroom with a walk-in closet and a second smaller closet attached to the master bathroom. Bedrooms 2 and 3 are just across the hall. On the other side of the house, just above the garage, is a 4th bedroom, which offers plenty of privacy. Stepping out back, there's a great deck for grilling and hosting your summertime get togethers! Additionally this home is close to bases, shopping, restaurants and is just a short drive to beautiful beaches. Call today to schedule your personal walk-through. This one-of-a-kind home won't last long. Seller is offering $8k Use as you choose!
